"english_summary": "The central government has increased passport application fees. The fee for a regular passport is now Rs 2500, up from Rs 1500, and for a Tatkal (urgent) passport, it is Rs 5000, up from Rs 3500. The fees for children under 18 have also increased, now requiring Rs 2500."
