"english_summary": "In Sriganganagar, a shop employee stole jewelry worth Rs 16 lakh from the house of former Gusai President Seema Pediwal at 3 AM on Wednesday night. Police acted swiftly and arrested the employee, Rajesh Kumar, from his home with the stolen jewelry. Rajesh had been working for Pediwal for seven years. Further investigation is underway to determine the motive behind the theft and if any accomplices were involved."
